<HEAD>SECT. III. Of Restoration by Jesus Christ, and Faith in him.</HEAD>
<P>WE believe, That Jesus Christ is the <NOTE N="(a)" PLACE="marg">Prov. 8 23 24. c<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">p. 3.4. Mich. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">.2. Jo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">.25. Ne<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">. 9.<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">. Jo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">. 1<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">.26.</NOTE> Son of God, and the only begotten of God from Ever|lasting, and one God with the Father; and t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">at he was the Redeemer and Sa|viour of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hat be<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ie<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ed in him from the begi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ni<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">g of the Wo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ld, and gave them the ho<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">y Spi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">t to r<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">new &amp; san|ctifi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> them, and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hat this holy Spirit did <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">roceed f<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">om th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> Father &amp; from the Son.</P>
